t><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01623">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 13. 8. 1906</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01625">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 8. 9. 1906</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01620">Schnitzler, Salten an Hofmannsthal, 3. 8. 1906</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01625">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 8. 9. 1906</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
